metadata.name: #0 SciFi Stoner Cats Poster
metadata.description: Stoner Cats movie posters were hand-drawn by pixar alumnus and Stoner Cats creator Ash Brannon, to celebrate blowing through the 50% milestone and selling out in minutes. Three styles, each inspired by iconic movie posters of their time, randomly assigned and claimable by Stoner Cats holders for gas only.
